SUMMARY:Columbia Market House
DESCRIPTION:MORE THAN A MARKET\nWelcome to the Columbia Market House\, the Riverlands’ center for fresh produce\, specialty foods\, and Saturday morning market traditions. Established in 1869 to connect locals and farmers\, Market has returned with year-round vendor stands\, a restaurant\, and an event space. \nColumbia Market House is a vital center for fresh produce\, specialty foods\, and community experience. Established in 1869 to connect citizens and farmers\, the Market has returned with a year-round farmers market\, restaurant\, and event space.
URL:https://lancasterpa.com/events-calendar/columbia-market-house/2026-03-28/
LOCATION:Discover Columbia\, Columbia\, 17512\, United States
CATEGORIES:Columbia PA,Farmers Markets,Food & Beverage Events,Shopping
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://lancasterpa.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/Columbia-Market-House-Events.png
