DESCRIPTION:Please join us for our 6th Annual Easter Egg Hunt!\nThis is a public event for children ages 0-12 years old.\nTake your own photos with the Easter Bunny  Bunny will be available for pictures beginning at 9:30AMAllergy friendly and candy-free! Each age group will have eggs with GOLDEN TICKETS for large prizes.\nTacoRv Truck with be serving delicious breakfast sandwiches and Mocha Motion Coffee will be there for everyone’s coffee needs Hope to see you all there!\n\nLOCATION: LITITZ SPRINGS PARK (playground side)0-2 year olds 10:00AM3-5 year olds 10:10AM6-8 year olds 10:20AM9-12 year olds 10:30AMSensory & Special needs 10:40AM\n\nAdditional Fun Things To Do in Lancaster?\n\n\nKids’ Attractions\nFamily Attractions\nAmish Attractions\n\n\n\nThings To Do for Adults and Couples\nHistorical & Educational\nIndoor Things To Do\n\n\n\nTheater\, Music\, & The Arts\nMud Sales\nEvents Calendar\n\n \nTake a look at many more Attractions offered throughout Lancaster County this summer!
