DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260328T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260328T213000
DTSTAMP:20260327T180207
CREATED:20260304T162808Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260304T162809Z
UID:56699-1774728000-1774733400@visitlancastercity.com
SUMMARY:Black to the Future: A Legendary Round Table
DESCRIPTION:Straight from the time machine\, these icons and pioneers are here for one hilariously historic night! \n\n\n\nPowerful figures from throughout history will gather together at the nexus of culture that is Lancaster Improv Players theater for a meeting of the minds previously thought impossible. Clearly\, they didn’t know about improv comedy. Through improv\, anything is possible; even time travel! \n\n\n\nHosted by Lancaster theater luminary\, Andrew “Sarge” Dixon \n\n\n\n“Impossible is just a word thrown around by small men who find it easier to live in the world they’ve been given than to explore the power they have to change it. Impossible is not a fact. It’s an opinion. Impossible is potential. Impossible is temporary. Impossible is nothing.” \n\n\n\n-Muhammad Ali \n\n\n\n$15 at the door \n\n\n\nBYOB \n\n\n\nDue to the size of our theater\, there is a quick turnover time between our scheduled shows. If you purchase tickets to both events on Saturday evening\, you will be asked to wait outside during the break so that the next team can warm up before the audience returns.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/black-to-the-future-a-legendary-round-table/
LOCATION:Lancaster Improv Players\, 16 S Prince St\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Theatre
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/black-to-the-future.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Lancaster Improv Players":MAILTO:kate@lancasterimprovplayers.org
END:VEVENT
