SUMMARY:Norristown Farm Park
DESCRIPTION:Walking Tails\nThis walk is 2.25 miles for the first loop (gre
 en trail on the map) and 2.0 miles for a second OPTIONAL loop (purple trai
 l on the map). Both loops are on a paved surface. About 50% of the first l
 oop is shady\, the second loop is primarily in the sun.\n\nStart Time: We 
 will start hiking promptly at the scheduled time.\n\nDuration of the walk 
 – depends on the people and dogs in the group. We frequently end up walk
 ing in smaller packs based on the comfort level of the participants.\n\nIn
  the past this walk has taken from 1 to 2 hours\, depending on whether we 
 do both loops.\n\nPlease remember pooh bags and that your dog must be on a
  leash that is no more than 10 feet long.\n\nNOTICE: By attending this eve
 nt you are agreeing that YOU ARE RESPONSIBLE FOR YOUR OWN SAFETY AT ALL TI
 MES. The hike leader and other members cannot be held responsible for any 
 damages\, accidents\, or liabilities incurred while hiking with us.\n\nNor
 ristown Farm Park Map (http://www.montcopa.org/DocumentCenter/View/3433)
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/walking-tails/events/313904283/
