 re a realistic mini-grocery market complete with colorful play food\, shop
 ping baskets\, cash registers\, and more. They can shop\, stock shelves\, 
 or take on the role of a cashier\, fostering creativity\, social interacti
 on\, and basic math skills in a fun\, welcoming environment.This drop-in p
 rogram is perfect for children ages 2–7 and their families. No registrat
 ion is required—just come by and let your little ones experience the joy
  of imaginative play!Come play\, learn\, and grow at the library! Each fam
 ily group must include a responsible adult in the room at all times. This 
 program is for children 2 to 7 years old only! While other ages are welcom
 e in the room\, we kindly ask that the play area and toys remain reserved 
 exclusively for the intended age group to ensure a safe environment for yo
 ung participants.
LOCATION:Manheim Township\, MTP Lapp Story Silo
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/market-monday-155846
X-SOURCE:Lancaster Libraries
END:VEVENT
