BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Lancaster Libraries": "https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/book-club-reader-bella-monthly-twilight-book-club-adults-162379"}
X-SOURCE-ID:lancaster_libraries
SUMMARY:This is the Book Club of a Reader\, Bella: a Monthly Twilight Book
  Club (for adults)
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260330T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260330T194500
UID:af0b8e60cca99b187f582fafcb3f3649@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Book Club\, Community\, Discussion\, Adults\, Seniors\n\nWheth
 er you were Team Edward\, Team Jacob\, or Team Bella-Gets-A-Grip\, it's ti
 me to head back to Forks! Join us for an adult-only book club where we rev
 isit Stephenie Meyer's Twilight Saga with the benefit of hindsight\, a lit
 tle bit of maturity\, and a lot of humor. We'll discuss the cultural pheno
 menon\, the questionable relationship dynamics\, and why-- despite everyth
 ing-- we still can't put it down. Relive the 2008 mania. We’re talking b
 ody glitter\, the iconic soundtrack\, and the blue tint that defined a gen
 eration.We’ll take a deep dive into the ~complicated romance of Edward a
 nd Bella. Is it undying love\, or do we need to stage an intervention?Team
  Edward vs. Team Jacob. Have your loyalties shifted now that you're an adu
 lt? (Spoiler: It’s okay to choose Mike Newton).From the logistics of vam
 pire baseball to the sheer audacity of the name Renesmee\, no stone--or sp
 ider monkey-- will be left unturned.🍎 18+\, please! 🧛 🐺
LOCATION:Manheim Township\, MTP Morgan Center A
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/book-club-reader-bella-m
 onthly-twilight-book-club-adults-162379
X-SOURCE:Lancaster Libraries
END:VEVENT
