X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Visit Lancaster City": "https://visitlancastercity.com/event/savage-cabaret-electric-parlor/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:visitlancastercity
X-SOURCE:Visit Lancaster City
X-SOURCE-URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260403T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260403T220000
DTSTAMP:20260327T180207
CREATED:20260326T202004Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260326T202005Z
UID:57079-1775242800-1775253600@visitlancastercity.com
SUMMARY:Savage Cabaret: Electric Parlor
DESCRIPTION:Experience burlesque\, drag and comedy as they take over City Hall at West Art\, where stained glass windows and soaring wooden beams set the stage for an unforgettable evening of glamour\, expression and mischief. \n\n\n\nThis special edition of Savage Cabaret brings the magic closer than ever before. With only 45 small tables per show\, audiences will experience vaudeville the way it was meant to be seen — intimate\, up close and personal. \n\n\n\nEach one-hour performance features a dazzling lineup of consisting of 3 burlesque artists\, one drag queen and one songstress\, creating a fast-paced\, high-energy cabaret experience that is as playful as it is intense. \n\n\n\nWhether you’re planning a group night out\, a memorable date\, or simply looking for something extraordinary to do in Lancaster\, Savage Cabaret: Electric Parlor offers a night unlike anything else in Central Pennsylvania. \n\n\n\nTables seat two guests with the option to add up to two more chairs. \n\n\n\nOnly 45 tables are available per show. Once they’re gone\, they’re gone. \n\n\n\nReserve yours now and get ready to feel the buzz. \n\n\n\nFriday Night Lineup: \n\n\n\nHosted by  Wilfredo (NYC) \n\n\n\nBurlesque by London St. Juniper (DC) \n\n\n\nBurlesque by Kalypso Kraken (MD) \n\n\n\nHula from Caresse Deville (PHL) \n\n\n\nDrag from Diane Decay (717) \n\n\n\nSong by Starlight DeVil (NJ) \n\n\n\n… and bizarro clown energy from Peetie Esdee
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/savage-cabaret-electric-parlor/
LOCATION:West Art Community Center\, 816 Buchanan Ave\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Music and Dance
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/cityoflancasterpa-242134369851055-6502726183274556174-Untitled-design.png
END:VEVENT
