SUMMARY:Read Aloud with Pepper the Dog!
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260404T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260404T150000
UID:663f5115d1cef97974a7b6ee22a5292a@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Community\, Health & Wellness\, Children\, Everyone\n\nDid you
  know?  Research shows that therapy dogs help people to improve attention 
 span\, focus\, & well-being and that reluctant readers enjoy and benefit f
 rom reading aloud to a pup. Children of all ages (accompanied by their par
 ent or other caregiver) are invited to spend some time with and read aloud
  to Pepper\, a friendly and adorable Labrador Retriever who will be accomp
 anied by Mrs. Carol Stark. (Pepper has a Canine Good Citizen certificate f
 rom the American Kennel Club and is certified for excellence at the Advanc
 ed level by PAWS for People.)No registration required.
LOCATION:Eastern Lancaster County
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/read-aloud-pepper-dog-15
 2782
