X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Visit Lancaster City": "https://visitlancastercity.com/event/revolution-the-music-of-the-beatles-a-symphonic-experience-with-lso/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:visitlancastercity
X-SOURCE:Visit Lancaster City
X-SOURCE-URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260407T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260407T220000
DTSTAMP:20260327T180207
CREATED:20251024T122643Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251024T122644Z
UID:55388-1775588400-1775599200@visitlancastercity.com
SUMMARY:Revolution: The Music of The Beatles - A Symphonic Experience with LSO!
DESCRIPTION:Experience The Beatles like never before as the Lancaster Symphony Orchestra joins top vocalists and rock musicians to perform sweeping orchestral arrangements of more than 25 of the Fab Four’s top hits. Revolution immerses audiences in legendary songs like Ticket to Ride\, Penny Lane\, All You Need Is Love\, Get Back\, Here Comes the Sun\, and Hey Jude (and many more)—accompanied by stunning video\, animation\, and hundreds of rare and unseen photos from the archives of the band’s official fan magazine\, The Beatles Book Monthly. Grammy-winner Jeff Tyzik’s new arrangements\, transcribed and arranged from the original master recordings at Abbey Road\, bring The Beatles’ magic to life in this celebration of the band’s enduring legacy. Doors open at 5:30 pm. Click on the link below for ticket information or feel free to call the box office at 717-291-6440 ext 1.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/revolution-the-music-of-the-beatles-a-symphonic-experience-with-lso/
LOCATION:Lancaster County Convention Center\, 25 South Queen Street\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17602\, United States
CATEGORIES:Music and Dance
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/Revolution.jpg
GEO:40.0375921;-76.3051649
