 nd East Lampeter residents and on Friday\, April 3rd for residents of othe
 r municipalities.Storytime PoliciesProgram Limits - Patrons are limited to
  one session of multiple session programs per week.Cancellations- Please c
 heck your email prior to departing to verify that the program has not been
  cancelled.No Show – Patrons failing to cancel their registration for mo
 re than 2 library programs in a month will be restricted from registering 
