  for those on the waiting list to be notified of their change in registrat
 ion status.Late Arrivals – Please arrive 10 minutes prior to the start o
 f the program to allow for parking and other circumstances. The program wi
 ll begin promptly at the designated time. At this time\, your spot will be
  forfeited to those on the wait list who will be granted entry. If spots r
 emain\, registrants may be allowed into the program. However\, registrants
  will not be permitted to enter the program 5 minutes past the start time.
