DESCRIPTION:Technology Class\, Adults\, Seniors\n\nDo you need help withWr
 iting\, creating\, or updating a resume?Applying for jobs online? Filling 
 out clearances/forms to begin employment?Learning how to write\, reply to\
 , and delete emails?Using Microsoft Word\, Excel\, Power Point\, or Outloo
 k more proficiently?Using virtual tools such as Zoom or Microsoft Teams?Le
 arning how to stay safe while shopping online?Creating and using an email 
 account?Turning on a computer and connecting to the Internet?Using the Int
 ernet safely and protecting your information?Unbox Your New TechConsider s
 topping in at the Columbia Public Library for FREE one-on-one assistance. 
 Doran is available every Tuesday\, Wednesday\, and Thursday 10:00am - 3:00
 pm to assist you.Phillip is available Monday\, Wednesday\, Friday 10:00am 
 - 1:00pm to assist you. Bring your own laptop or use one of ours at the li
