BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Visit Lancaster City": "https://visitlancastercity.com/event/friday-night-improv-go-bulldogs-3/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:visitlancastercity
X-SOURCE:Visit Lancaster City
X-SOURCE-URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260410T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260410T200000
DTSTAMP:20260327T180207
CREATED:20260318T151313Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260318T151314Z
UID:56935-1775847600-1775851200@visitlancastercity.com
SUMMARY:Friday Night Improv: GO BULLDOGS!
DESCRIPTION:A community-wide conspiracy designed to bring laughter to Lancaster \n\n\n\nJoin us for a casual night out in downtown Lancaster City that will have you rolling in the aisles…well\, aisle! \n\n\n\nGO BULLDOGSIt’s tradition around these parts that whenever you hear someone say “Go Bulldogs!”\, you have to reply “GO BULLDOGS!” GBD is Lancaster Improv Players longest running team; each show is a randomized selection of players from our entire community of students\, coaches\, and performers. that means once you finish an improv course at LIP\, you can be a Bulldog\, too! \n\n\n\nBYOB & Pay What You Will \n\n\n\nDoors at 6:45PM\, show at 7:00PM \n\n\n\nDue to the size of our theater\, there is a quick turnover time between our scheduled shows. If you purchase tickets to both events on Friday evening\, you will be asked to wait outside during the break so that the next team can warm up before the audience returns. \n\n\n\nLANCASTER IMPROV PLAYERS is an intimate black box venue located in the heart of Lancaster City. With a capacity of approximately 30 guests\, that means this Lancaster comedy club is entirely front row. Not a nosebleed in sight! After all\, BYOB is just a drink special you never get tired of.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/friday-night-improv-go-bulldogs-3/
LOCATION:Lancaster Improv Players\, 16 S Prince St\, Lancaster\, Pennsylvania\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Theatre
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/GO-BULLDOGS-2nd-friday-event-2.jpg
ORGANIZER;CN="Lancaster Improv Players":MAILTO:kate@lancasterimprovplayers.org
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Visit Lancaster City": "https://visitlancastercity.com/event/shawan-rice-the-quiet-riders/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:visitlancastercity
X-SOURCE:Visit Lancaster City
X-SOURCE-URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260410T193000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260410T210000
DTSTAMP:20260327T180207
CREATED:20251024T181615Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251024T181616Z
UID:55461-1775849400-1775854800@visitlancastercity.com
SUMMARY:Shawan Rice & The Quiet Riders
DESCRIPTION:Treat yourself to a night under the stars featuring the best of local music! Soulful\, rootsy\, unique: these innovative artists and Central PA natives deliver inventive tunes that will have you grooving in your seat. Originally from the midstate\, Shawan Rice toured the U.S. before relocating to New Orleans\, where her captivating voice has made her a staple in the city’s vibrant music scene. Lancaster-based band The Quiet Riders share a deep love for American music\, earning them a Central PA Music Award for “Best Funk Band” in 2024. Taking place in the stunning glass pyramid-topped Atrium of the Ware Center\, the “Lancaster Loves” series features the best in local music across a variety of genres in a lively cabaret setting.
URL:https://visitlancastercity.com/event/shawan-rice-the-quiet-riders/
LOCATION:The Ware Center – Millersville University\, 42 N. Prince Street\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17603\, United States
CATEGORIES:Music and Dance
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://visitlancastercity.com/wp-content/uploads/2026.04.10-Shawan-Rice-The-Quiet-Riders.jpg
END:VEVENT
