SUMMARY:Teen BYOB: Bedazzle Your Own Book
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260411T130000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260411T150000
UID:f2496b045014ef6a948877fb12a70e87@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Arts & Crafts\, Teens\n\nBring your favorite book and give it 
 some sparkle! Teens (ages 13-18) are invited to a fun\, creative afternoon
  where you can bedazzle your own book cover using rhinestones and gems pro
 vided by the library. Whether you want a subtle shimmer or full-on glam\, 
 you can design a book that completely matches your style.Hang out with fri
 ends\, get creative\, and leave with a book that you will treasure forever
 !Note: Please bring a book that you are comfortable decorating - supplies 
 will be provided\, but books will not.Registration will open at 9:00AM on 
 Wednesday\, March 25th for Manheim Township and East Lampeter residents an
 d on Wednesday\, April 1st for residents of other municipalities.LIBRARY P
 ROGRAM POLICIES:Designated Ages – Please adhere to the age restrictions 
 designated on your registration. Only children in that age range will be a
 dmitted.Registration Requirements – To help us manage our space\, please
  register every person who will be attending\, including siblings.No Show 
 – Patrons failing to cancel their registration for more than 2 library p
 rograms in a month will be restricted from registering for future programs
  for a period of one month’s time. Please cancel your registrations at l
 east 2 hours prior to the start of the program to allow for those on the w
 aiting list to be notified of their change in registration status.Late Arr
 ivals – Please arrive 10 minutes prior to the start of the program to al
 low for parking and other circumstances. The program will begin promptly a
 t the designated time. At this time\, your spot will be forfeited to those
  on the wait list who will be granted entry. If spots remain\, registrants
  may be allowed into the program. However\, registrants will not be permit
 ted to enter the program 5 minutes past the start time.
LOCATION:Manheim Township\, MTP Morgan Center A
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/teen-byob-bedazzle-your-
 own-book-166300
X-SOURCE:Lancaster Libraries
END:VEVENT
