SUMMARY:Beginner Birder Trip to Riverfront Park
DESCRIPTION:Contact: Sarah Gotwols 717-940-3804 (call/text) or sarahann71880@gmail.com \nBeginner Birder field trip at Riverfront Park and journey along the Northwest River Trail along the Susquehanna River. This trip is designed for individuals who would like to experience birding for the first time or would like to further their birding observation skills. Our target species will include a variety of spring migrants\, such as warblers and other songbirds. Hawk species and Bald Eagles are often in the area as well. Please contact Sarah Gotwols 717-940-3804 (call/text) or sarahann71880@gmail.com if you plan to attend.
