X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Lancaster Libraries": "https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/toddler-time-148692"}
X-SOURCE-ID:lancaster_libraries
SUMMARY:Toddler Time
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260414T101500
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260414T104500
UID:09bdd03bea11973368c51e386af9c21a@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Storytime\, Toddlers\n\nA time for Toddlers with their grown-u
 p\, dedicated to stories\, discovery and exploring!  (18 months to 36 mont
 hs\, with adult. Other family members welcome.)Adults attending with their
  child(ren) do NOT need to register. Please add any additional registrants
  to your registration if more than one child that will be participating in
  the program.Registration will open at 9:00AM on Wednesday\, April 1st for
  Manheim Township and East Lampeter residents and on Friday\, April 3rd fo
 r residents of other municipalities.Storytime PoliciesNo Show – Patrons 
 failing to cancel their registration for more than 2 library programs in a
  month will be restricted from registering for future programs for a perio
 d of one month’s time. Please cancel your registrations at least 2 hours
  prior to the start of the program to allow for those on the waiting list 
 to be notified of their change in registration status.Late Arrivals – Pl
 ease arrive 10 minutes prior to the start of the program to allow for park
 ing and other circumstances. The program will begin promptly at the design
 ated time. At this time\, your spot will be forfeited to those on the wait
  list who will be granted entry. If spots remain\, registrants may be allo
 wed into the program. However\, registrants will not be permitted to enter
  the program 5 minutes past the start time.Accompanying Adults – This pr
 ogram is for adults and children to enjoy together. Please plan to attend 
 and be engaged with your child. Drop offs will not be permitted.Cancellati
 ons- Please check your email prior to departing to verify that the program
  has not been cancelled.Program Limits - Patrons are limited to one sessio
 n of multiple session programs per week.
LOCATION:Manheim Township\, MTP Lapp Story Silo
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/toddler-time-148692
X-SOURCE:Lancaster Libraries
END:VEVENT
