DESCRIPTION:Community\, Gaming\, Adults\, Seniors\n\nGo from "What's a Bam
 ?" to "Mahjong!" in this five-week intensive designed for true beginners. 
 We’ll dive into the beautiful tiles\, the National Mah Jongg League card
 \, and the fast-paced strategy that makes the game a total blast. By the f
 inal week\, you’ll be playing with confidence and style!The Full-Table C
 ommitment: Because each lesson builds directly on the last\, signing up fo
 r the first session means you are committed to the full five-week journey.
  Please ensure you can attend every class to keep the "puzzle" together fo
 r the whole group.Schedule (1-3pm):April 16April 23April 30May 7May 14New 
 Players Only\, Please!: To keep things fair and give everyone a shot at th
 e tiles\, this course is strictly for true beginners. If you've already ta
 ken a Mahjong class at any library branch in the county\, we ask that you 
 leave this spot open for someone who hasn't had the chance to learn yet. W
 e love your enthusiasm\, but this specific table is reserved for those who
  are brand new to the game.
