X-SOURCE-URLS:{"American Music Theatre": "https://amtshows.com/show/folsom-prison-experience-a-johnny-cash-music-dramatic-production/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:amtshows
X-SOURCE:American Music Theatre
X-SOURCE-URL:https://amtshows.com/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260419T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260419T150000
DTSTAMP:20260328T230355
CREATED:20250908T133059Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251020T130250Z
UID:10001810-1776610800-1776610800@amtshows.com
SUMMARY:Folsom Prison Experience - A Johnny Cash Music/Dramatic Production
DESCRIPTION:Tickets: $24 $34 $44 \nPrepare to step back in time and immerse yourself in the unforgettable atmosphere of the legendary 1968 Johnny Cash show at Folsom Prison\, where the spirit of that historic day springs to life. \nAs the doors swing open\, you’ll find yourself instantly transformed into an inmate\, ready to embark on a captivating firsthand experience. Marvel at the commanding presence of Johnny Cash himself\, joined by the incomparable June Carter and the melodious harmonies of the Statler Brothers. Sense the palpable tension as the watchful warden and his guards maintain order within the prison walls. \nLeading you through this extraordinary journey is the ever-serious emcee\, Hugh Cherry. Get ready to be transported\, as you become an integral part of this immersive tribute\, capturing the raw energy and soul that made the Folsom Prison performance truly remarkable. A memorable show for all ages. \nFor certain concerts\, audience members may prefer to stand or dance\, especially when encouraged by the artist to do so. Guest expectations differ\, so we simply ask all attendees to extend mutual respect toward one another and maintain awareness of those around them. Our staff will only intervene in matters of safety or when behavior is deemed unruly\, combative\, or disruptive to the overall performance. \n  \n 
URL:https://amtshows.com/show/folsom-prison-experience-a-johnny-cash-music-dramatic-production/
LOCATION:American Music Theatre\, 2425 Lincoln Hwy East\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17605\, United States
CATEGORIES:Arts & Theatre,Celebrity Concerts
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://amtshows.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/FPE_Concessions-Events-and-News-for-Website-1920x1080-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
