 ealth & Wellness\, Presentation\, Babies\, Toddlers\, Children\, Tweens\, 
 Teens\, Adults\, Seniors\, Everyone\n\nThere’s nothing quite like the sm
 ell of fresh-baked cookies to bring a community together. We’re excited 
 to invite you to our upcoming Community Cookie Night—an evening dedicate
 d to local leaders\, community partners\, great conversation\, and\, most 
 importantly\, the ultimate cookie showdown!Join the FunWhether you want to
  enter the contest or just enjoy the treats\, we’d love to see you there
 .Note: As of today\, March 26\, we still need three more contestants to fi
 ll our roster. Don't be shy—show us what you've got!Contest DetailsThe B
 ake: Prepare one cookie flavor of your choice.The Quantity: We ask for thr
 ee dozen cookies so there are plenty for everyone to sample.The Event: Bri
 ng your cookies on the night of the event\; they will be put on display fo
 r our patrons to taste and judge!How to RegisterTo enter the contest\, ple
 ase call the front desk with your name and phone number and let them know 
 you want to compete.Thank you for being such an important part of our comm
 unity. We can't wait to see (and taste) what you bake!
