BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Lancaster Libraries": "https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/book-club-reader-bella-monthly-twilight-book-club-adults-new-moon-edition-170113"}
X-SOURCE-ID:lancaster_libraries
SUMMARY:This is the Book Club of a Reader\, Bella: a Monthly Twilight Book
  Club (for adults): New Moon Edition
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260427T180000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260427T194500
UID:7ee802f925ca2b4512cfc913eee88759@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Book Club\, Community\, Discussion\, Adults\, Seniors\n\nWheth
 er you’re still waiting for the hole in your chest to heal or you’re j
 ust here for the motorcycles and the angst\, it’s time to head back to t
 he rainiest town in America. Join us for an adult-only book club where we 
 revisit Stephenie Meyer’s New Moon—the era of heartbreak\, questionabl
 e cliff-diving\, and the ultimate supernatural rebound. We’re revisiting
  the saga with the benefit of hindsight\, a bit of maturity\, and a health
 y dose of humor.Relive the 2009 mania. We’re talking about the cinematic
  depression\, the flannel shirts\, and the movie soundtrack that made us a
 ll feel way too much. We will take a deep dive into Edward’s "it’s for
  your own good" ghosting to decide if it was noble protection or if Bella 
 should have checked into therapy instead of a garage.18+ only\, please🍎
 ♟️🩸💔
LOCATION:Manheim Township\, MTP Morgan Center B
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/book-club-reader-bella-m
 onthly-twilight-book-club-adults-new-moon-edition-170113
X-SOURCE:Lancaster Libraries
END:VEVENT
