LAST-MODIFIED:20260131T194143Z
UID:10000024-1777593600-1777766399@stevensandsmithcenter.org
SUMMARY:Grand Opening Weekend of the Stevens & Smith Center
DESCRIPTION:It’s the moment we’ve all been waiting for: the Grand Opening of the Thaddeus Stevens & Lydia Hamilton Smith Center for History and Democracy! \nJoin LancasterHistory for a weekend celebration\, including a ribbon cutting\, Grand Opening Gala\, and a family-friendly community block party! \nMore information to come!
URL:https://stevensandsmithcenter.org/event/grand-opening-weekend/
LOCATION:The Stevens & Smith Center\, 13-15 East Vine Street\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17602\, United States
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Stevens & Smith Center": "https://stevensandsmithcenter.org/event/ribbon/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:stevensandsmithcenter
X-SOURCE:Stevens & Smith Center
X-SOURCE-URL:https://stevensandsmithcenter.org/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260501T080000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260501T100000
DTSTAMP:20260328T230353
CREATED:20260313T202503Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260316T151058Z
UID:10000025-1777622400-1777629600@stevensandsmithcenter.org
SUMMARY:Grand Opening Ribbon Cutting Ceremony
DESCRIPTION:Opening on May 1\, 2026\, in the heart of downtown Lancaster\, the restored historic properties once owned by Thaddeus Stevens and his partner Lydia Hamilton Smith are re-envisioned as a state-of-the-art museum and education space. Innovative exhibits\, created with leading historians and designers\, confront slavery\, freedom\, and the ongoing fight for equality in America. LancasterHistory—together with many collaborative partners—are eager to welcome the public for this once-in-a-generation moment for our community\, a celebration as bold as the history it honors!\n\nThe excitement kicks off Friday morning as we officially open the Stevens & Smith Center with a celebratory ribbon-cutting! Doors open at 8am for coffee\, light fare\, and mingling. At 9am\, the program begins with inspiring remarks and special guest performances that set the stage for a powerful new chapter.\n\nThis event is free and open to the entire community; we can’t wait to celebrate with you! Please RSVP so we can ensure ample seating and plenty of breakfast items for everyone. Join us as we mark this historic moment together and open the doors to something extraordinary!\n\nRSVP for the Ribbon Cutting
URL:https://stevensandsmithcenter.org/event/ribbon/
LOCATION:The Stevens & Smith Center\, 13-15 East Vine Street\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17602\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/png:https://stevensandsmithcenter.org/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/Ribbon-Cutting_web.png
END:VEVENT
