UID:da437467c943a497f7504068dd7f798d@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Storytime\, Babies\, Toddlers\, Children\n\nJoin us for a swee
 t and silly Diabetes Storytime\, filled with stories\, songs\, and a craft
 y surprise! In a kid-friendly way\, we'll explore what diabetes is and how
  it can be fun! Everyone is welcome\, whether you or your child has diabet
 es\, or you just want to learn more.All ages · Walk-ins welcome!
