DESCRIPTION:Finance\, Virtual\, Adults\, Seniors\n\nJoin us for a virtual 
 and complimentary educational seminar designed to help you feel more confi
 dent and informed about your financial future. This online session is faci
 litated by two experienced female financial advisors who are passionate ab
 out empowering individuals to take control of their finances. The seminar 
 will give you the tools you need to make informed financial decisions.Our 
 hosts will share their expertise about practical\, real-life financial top
 ics - from saving\, investing\, to retirement planning\, social security\,
  as well as life insurance and disability income insurance.Thank you for r
 egistering.➡️ We will be using Zoom to host this program. You will nee
 d either a computer with a microphone and webcam\, or a smartphone to conn
 ect. After you register\, you will receive the meeting link via email.Shei
 la Stotler & Tara Hauber are registered representatives of and offers secu
 rities\, investment advisory and financial planning services through MML I
 nvestors Services\, LLC. Member SIPC (www.SIPC.org) SupervisoryAddress:100
  Sterling Pkwy\, #307\, Mechanicsburg\, PA 17050. 717.791.3300CRN202808-93
 01533
