 ied of their change in registration status.Late Arrivals – Please arrive
  10 minutes prior to the start of the program to allow for parking and oth
 er circumstances. The program will begin promptly at the designated time. 
 At this time\, your spot will be forfeited to those on the wait list who w
 ill be granted entry. If spots remain\, registrants may be allowed into th
 e program. However\, registrants will not be permitted to enter the progra
 m 5 minutes past the start time.Accompanying Adults – This program is fo
 r adults and children to enjoy together. Please plan to attend and be enga
 ged with your child. Drop offs will not be permitted.Cancellations- Please
