X-SOURCE-URLS:{"Lancaster Libraries": "https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/parachute-play-148012"}
X-SOURCE-ID:lancaster_libraries
SUMMARY:Parachute Play
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260511T101500
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260511T104500
UID:33a867dfb859a3aa432defca094f0b67@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Storytime\, Toddlers\, Children\n\nJoin us for a cooperative m
 ovement program where we will use our imaginations while we play with a pa
 rachute! Stories and songs will be incorporated\, while we move about and 
 use our motor skills. A great activity for young children and their adults
  to come together and share an exciting and engaging play experience! (Mus
 t be 18 months-younger 3 years old with an adult\, adult involvement is re
 quired)Adults attending with their child(ren) do NOT need to register. Ple
 ase add any additional registrants to your registration if more than one c
 hild that will be participating in the program.Registration will open at 9
 :00AM on Wednesday\, April 29th for Manheim Township and East Lampeter res
 idents and on Friday\, May 1st for residents of other municipalities.Story
 time PoliciesNo Show – Patrons failing to cancel their registration for 
 more than 2 library programs in a month will be restricted from registerin
 g for future programs for a period of one month’s time. Please cancel yo
 ur registrations at least 2 hours prior to the start of the program to all
 ow for those on the waiting list to be notified of their change in registr
 ation status.Late Arrivals – Please arrive 10 minutes prior to the start
  of the program to allow for parking and other circumstances. The program 
 will begin promptly at the designated time. At this time\, your spot will 
 be forfeited to those on the wait list who will be granted entry. If spots
  remain\, registrants may be allowed into the program. However\, registran
 ts will not be permitted to enter the program 5 minutes past the start tim
 e.Accompanying Adults – This program is for adults and children to enjoy
  together. Please plan to attend and be engaged with your child. Drop offs
  will not be permitted.Cancellations- Please check your email prior to dep
 arting to verify that the program has not been cancelled.Program Limits - 
 Patrons are limited to one session of multiple session programs per week.
LOCATION:Manheim Township\, MTP Lapp Story Silo
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/parachute-play-148012
X-SOURCE:Lancaster Libraries
END:VEVENT
