DESCRIPTION:Community\, Adults\n\nJoin experts from Lancaster County Court
 s for semiweekly classes focused on basic life skills like computer usage\
 , resume building\, job searching\, math\, reading\, and writing. Take you
 r life in a new direction while working at the library in a calm\, neutral
  space with presenters that have been guiding individuals towards better o
 utcomes in different capacities throughout the corrections\, nonprofit\, a
 nd private world. These classes will continue through September 2026\, so 
 you can keep honing your skills for months to come.
