DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260515T101500
UID:e286ef00a99c7d1678feb89ecc2289c1@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Community\, Discussion\, Music\, Storytime\, Babies\n\nCome wi
 ggle\, giggle\, and grow with Miss Esther! Join us for 30 minutes of music
 al magic and sweet stories designed especially for your littlest sprouts. 
 We’ll be gathered in the meeting room—just a hop\, skip\, and a jump a
 cross from the circulation desk.This cozy circle is tailor-made for tiny e
 xplorers ages 6 to 24 months. Because we want to keep things comfy for eve
 ryone\, please only register your little ones in this age range. This is a
  special bonding time for you and your baby\, so grown-ups must stay for a
 ll the fun—no drop-offs\, please!Is your little one blooming into a big 
 kid? Once they hit their 2nd birthday (past 24 months)\, they’re ready t
 o join the adventure at Family Story Time! Join us there every Tuesday at 
 9:30 or 10:30 for even more library fun.A quick favor: If your plans chang
 e and you can't make it\, please let us know so another little friend can 
 join the circle as this class is usually booked up fast!
LOCATION:Manheim Community\, MAN Meeting Room
URL:https://calendar.lancasterlibraries.org/event/baby-time-spring-series-
 168938
