UID:f66fc537407ca598839af8e91e44e84e@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:STEM\, Children\n\nThe LEGO monthly program will tackle a vari
 ety of themes. Capping off each lesson will be a healthy amount of free-bu
 ild time. The program would be open to 12 children each month between the 
 ages of 6-10 years old. Third Saturday of each month from 10am-11 am.May's
  Theme: Freestyle Showcase - Participants will apply past skills to make t
