X-SOURCE-URLS:{"American Music Theatre": "https://amtshows.com/show/dick-foxs-golden-boys-starring-frankie-avalon-and-fabian-with-special-guest-tommy-cono-tributing-bobby-rydell/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:amtshows
X-SOURCE:American Music Theatre
X-SOURCE-URL:https://amtshows.com/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260517T150000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260517T150000
DTSTAMP:20260328T230355
CREATED:20251020T133057Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251215T202503Z
UID:10001825-1779030000-1779030000@amtshows.com
SUMMARY:Dick Fox’s Golden Boys starring Frankie Avalon and Fabian with special guest Tommy Cono Tributing Bobby Rydell
DESCRIPTION:Tickets: $69 $79 $89 $99 \nRelive the magic of the golden era of rock ‘n’ roll with Dick Fox’s Golden Boys! This unforgettable concert event reunites beloved teen idols of the late 1950s and early 1960s — Frankie Avalon and Fabian\, with special guest Tommy Cono (tributing Bobby Rydell) — for an evening packed with timeless hits\, charm\, and nostalgia. \nFrom Avalon’s chart-topping favorites like “Venus” and “Why” to Fabian’s energetic classics including “Turn Me Loose” and “Tiger\,” audiences will be transported back to a time when rock ‘n’ roll ruled the airwaves. With the addition of Tommy Cono’s smooth vocals and dynamic stage presence\, this show is a celebration of music that defined a generation. \nDick Fox’s Golden Boys blends unforgettable songs\, stories\, and humor into a joyful trip down memory lane — reminding us why these performers became household names and fan favorites around the world. \nFor certain concerts\, audience members may prefer to stand or dance\, especially when encouraged by the artist to do so. Guest expectations differ\, so we simply ask all attendees to extend mutual respect toward one another and maintain awareness of those around them. Our staff will only intervene in matters of safety or when behavior is deemed unruly\, combative\, or disruptive to the overall performance.
URL:https://amtshows.com/show/dick-foxs-golden-boys-starring-frankie-avalon-and-fabian-with-special-guest-tommy-cono-tributing-bobby-rydell/
LOCATION:American Music Theatre\, 2425 Lincoln Hwy East\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17605\, United States
CATEGORIES:Celebrity Concerts
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://amtshows.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/DFG_Concessions-Event-1920x1080-2.jpg
END:VEVENT
