 e Manheim Community Library!You will find us in the Breakout Room of the K
 reider Farms Cultural Center. Please join us for stories\, crafts\, and ac
 tivities!This program contains crafts that may be difficult for babies/tod
 dlers\, but we encourage you to try it! They may surprise you. We attempt 
 new motor skills often and encourage parents to help or step back as much 
 as they are comfortable.Family Story Time is a multiple registration type.
  Please register for any day you plan to attend. All (and only) children s
 hould be registered. This gives me an idea of how many chairs/tables\, as 
 well as supplies. Drop-offs will not be permitted\, and registration is re
 quired. If you realize you can't make it to Story Time\, please inform Est
 her Martin by emailing her at emartin@manheimlibrary.org. You can also cal
 l the front desk at (717)665-6700 Ext. 4200. Please let us know as soon as
  you can because we often have a waitlist\, and we want everyone to get th
 e chance to participate if possible.
