 r peers while learning the basics of how to plan ahead\, operate under a s
 trict budget\, be resourceful\, and communicate clearly and effectively in
  a low stress environment.Each Student who registers will be assigned a mo
 nth in 2026 (when they are available) for them to prepare their craft. Mis
 s Esther will give you a tour of her supplies\, explain your budget and ho
 w to submit receipts for reimbursement\, show you the basics needed for an
  instructions sheet\, and how to teach it in-person. Students are allowed 
 to be creative and choose whatever craft they enjoy already or want to lea
 rn next! When it is your month\, you will arrive early (5:30)\, set-up you
 r room\, make copies of your instructions\, and collect and set out your s
