UID:ef78059eef131b3224a53f65eb48bd3c@calendar.lancasterlibraries.org
DESCRIPTION:Community\, Health & Wellness\, Adults\, Seniors\n\nUnderstand
 ing Medicare can be difficult. PA-MEDI is here to help! We provide free\, 
 unbiased help to Medicare beneficiaries in Pennsylvania. We can assist ind
