X-SOURCE-URLS:{"American Music Theatre": "https://amtshows.com/show/lee-brice-2026/"}
X-SOURCE-ID:amtshows
X-SOURCE:American Music Theatre
X-SOURCE-URL:https://amtshows.com/events/
DTSTART;TZID=America/New_York:20260529T200000
DTEND;TZID=America/New_York:20260529T200000
DTSTAMP:20260328T230355
CREATED:20251117T143054Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20251120T133646Z
UID:10001833-1780084800-1780084800@amtshows.com
SUMMARY:Lee Brice
DESCRIPTION:Tickets: $99 $109 $119 $139\n \nGet ready for an unforgettable night of country music when Lee Brice takes the stage at American Music Theatre! Known for his powerhouse vocals\, heartfelt storytelling\, and chart-topping hits like “Hard to Love\,” “I Don’t Dance\,” “One of Them Girls\,” and “Rumor\,” Brice delivers a show packed with energy\, emotion\, and authenticity. \nA multi-platinum artist\, songwriter\, and CMA award-winner\, Lee Brice brings together the raw honesty of classic country with a modern edge that resonates with fans of all ages. Whether he’s performing tender ballads or high-energy anthems\, his passion and stage presence make every song hit home. \nFor certain concerts\, audience members may prefer to stand or dance\, especially when encouraged by the artist to do so. Guest expectations differ\, so we simply ask all attendees to extend mutual respect toward one another and maintain awareness of those around them. Our staff will only intervene in matters of safety or when behavior is deemed unruly\, combative\, or disruptive to the overall performance.
URL:https://amtshows.com/show/lee-brice-2026/
LOCATION:American Music Theatre\, 2425 Lincoln Hwy East\, Lancaster\, PA\, 17605\, United States
CATEGORIES:Celebrity Concerts
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://amtshows.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/LB_Concessions-Events-and-News-for-Website-1920x1080-1.jpg
END:VEVENT
