CREATED:20260325T111733Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260325T111826Z
UID:10001060-1780135200-1780156800@bird-in-hand.com
SUMMARY:Bird-in-Hand Artisan & Vintage Market
DESCRIPTION:Find handcrafted and vintage items\, antiques and more at this special shopping event! \nShop ‘til you drop\, then dine—all without leaving our village. Artisan Village is teaming up with Creative Rustic Furniture\, Modish Lancaster and Downingtown Vintage at Bird-in-Hand to bring you an outstanding day of treasure hunting in our village. Artisans from throughout the region and beyond will offer a wide variety of handcrafted merchandise. You’ll also be able to browse a broad selection of antiques and vintage items\, like jewelry\, clothing\, décor and much more. \nIn addition to the village shops\, you’ll find open-air vendors in front of and behind Artisan Village\, along the main walkway and around the parking lots and grassy areas near the other participating shops. Plus\, you’ll be within easy walking distance of Bird-in-Hand Farmers Market and the Bird-in-Hand Bakery & Cafe – so plan to join us and make a day of it. \nDate: Saturday\, May 30\nTime: 10 am–4 pm\nRain or shine \nInterested in being a vendor?  Click here for application.
URL:https://bird-in-hand.com/event/bird-in-hand-artisan-vintage-market/
LOCATION:Bird-in-Hand Artisan Village\, 2705 Old Philadelphia Pike\, Bird-in-Hand\, PA\, 17505\, United States
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://bird-in-hand.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/03/AVVendorFaire.jpg
END:VEVENT
