SUMMARY:Terrific Tuesdays: Week 2
DESCRIPTION:Splash into Terrific Tuesdays in Rader Park\, a four-week summer program for children ages 3-10 full of stories\, crafts\, and hands-on fun as we learn all about water. \nProgram Schedule (10–11:30 AM):June 16June 23June 30July 7 – Special Presentation by Lisa Sanchez\, Lancaster Parks Naturalist \nEach session will take place in beautiful Rader Park\, and snacks will be provided. Please note that a guardian must remain with their child throughout the program. \nRegistration is now open\, Click Here to Register!
