SUMMARY:2764 - Kids Cooking Camp - Food Trucks (Ages 7-15)
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a delicious Food Truck Adventure with our incredible kids’ instructor and artist\, Gwen Eberly! In this hands-on summer camp\, young chefs will build confidence in the kitchen while exploring bold flavors inspired by popular types of food trucks. Each day\, campers will learn essential cooking skills\, trying new ingredients\, and create fun\, street-food-style dishes in a creative and encouraging environment. \nHands on. Ages 7-15 \nDay 1 – 7/14 \nBurger Truck \n\nBeef Burger\nCrab Burger\nVeggie Burger\nHomemade Sauce – Chipotle Mayo\, Green Goddess\, BBQ\nToppings: Cheese\, Tomato\, Greens\, Onions\n\nDay 2 – 7/15 \nPotato Truck \n\nPotato Wedges\nSweet Potato Fries\nBaked Potatoes\nHomemade Sauces – Mojo\, Honey Dijon\, Fresh Salsa\nToppings: Chili\, Roasted Broccoli\, Cheese\n\nDay 3 – 7/16 \nShawarma Truck \n\nChicken Shawarma\nFalafels\nSeasoned Rice\nHummus\nBaba Ghanoush\nCucumber Tomato Salad
URL:https://zestchef.com/class/2764-kids-cooking-camp-food-trucks-ages-7-15/
LOCATION:Zest Cooking School\, 1180 Erbs Quarry Road\, Lititz\, PA\, 17543\, United States
CATEGORIES:Healthy Eating,Kids & Teens,Seasonal
ATTACH;FMTTYPE=image/jpeg:https://zestchef.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/02/kids-cooking-camp-2026-e1771378488261.jpeg
END:VEVENT
