SUMMARY:2765 -  Kids Camp: Picnicing and Glamping (ages 7-15)
DESCRIPTION:Join us for a fun-filled Picnic & Camping Cooking Adventure with our wonderful kids’ instructor and artist\, Gwen Eberly! In this hands-on summer camp\, young chefs will build confidence in the kitchen while learning to prepare foods inspired by picnics\, campouts\, and outdoor cooking traditions. Each day\, campers will explore new skills\, try fresh flavors\, and create kid-friendly dishes perfect for sharing\, all in a creative\, supportive environment designed to spark curiosity and independence in the kitchen. \nHands on. Ages 7-15 \nDay 1 – 7/21 \n\nTurkey\, Cheese and Basil Pesto Wrap\nRainbow Veggie Wraps\nShredded Potato Salad\nTrail Mix\nHomemade Marshmallows\n\nDay 2 – 7/22 \n\nTaco Salad \nGrilled Corn with Cilantro Lime Dressing\nGuacamole\nS’mores Tarts with Homemade Marshmallows\n\nDay 3 – 7/23 \n\nEgg Salad Sandwich\nPressed Italian Sandwich\nPasta Salad with Tangy Vinaigrette\nChocolate Brownies
URL:https://zestchef.com/class/2765-kids-camp-picnicing-and-glamping-ages-7-15/
LOCATION:Zest Cooking School\, 1180 Erbs Quarry Road\, Lititz\, PA\, 17543\, United States
